message: /* Preston Corbell */ What are you talking about this person has had a page on wiki for many years. Is credited in over 80 studio level projects which are clearly stated on the most reliable source for accurate movie credits. I will contribute more current sources, but please there are 1,000's of articles to delete before this one that have zero notoriety. It's great to ask for current resources but be consistent and get rid of all the garage articles first.
Added specifics about the referenced scene to make it easier to find.
